{"tid":1440144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［好鬼］突然咁多post屌機場無用 請大家小心","createTime":"2019-08-10T10:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T13:51:47.000Z","uid":9394,"like":184,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb426a1fda0581c55e3a6674fd1faeb2e424735","tid":1440144,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"出面好多post係咁屌機場無用 又話要升級<br />\n你要勇武既咪勇武 無需要攻擊其他運動 <br />\n機場手足記住 唔好鳩坐 多啲同遊客宣傳/叫口號就可以<br />\n其他攻擊運動既post唔洗推 由得佢地就好"},{"pid":"8dd412eb8428c52a243d65ff45e29051a006e048","tid":1440144,"uid":87780,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老味各有各做不分化不割蓆呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要各位肯企出嚟就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f909dd979252e054f625fed8c478f5f7a6cfcfcd","tid":1440144,"uid":6003,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"同撚意呀<br />\n尋晚留左機場兩個幾鐘<br />\n其實係無間斷向到港旅客叫口號<br />\n未見有膠化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38e737f08e868fb9235009025cd0bc335b7be77","tid":1440144,"uid":9394,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"重申一次 唔係想割 但其他人都唔好割機場手足<br />\n各有各做<br />\n有好多和理非去機場做野有用過出去好多"},{"pid":"02c42e94579e34df2701e3ba6a4218de3ca7f027","tid":1440144,"uid":140924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"尋晚有去機場，我就覺得幾好<br />\n有遊客都會收下文宣，有啲都會停下望下影下相<br />\n現場亦都有國際媒體，今日bbc都報左好似<br />\n無人知有無用，咩都試下，仲唔會損失手足，百利而無一害，個人覺得<br />\n<br />\n係機場保安辛苦啲，部分會表現少少不耐煩，我覺得都可以理解，大家可以幫下手喺現場維持下秩序疏導下人流